    <body.head>
      <hedline>
        <hl1>He Just Said No -- To the Drug War</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Sandra Burlingame letter on Matthew Miller's August 20 article supports New Mexico Gov Gary Johnson for taking unpopular stand on illegal drugs (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>How refreshing! A politician who takes a public stand on an unpopular issue. Perhaps Gary Johnson's courage will provoke study of the results of legislation in countries that have decriminalized drugs and an open discussion of the ramifications of such legislation in our own country.</p>
        <p>Sandra Burlingame  Portland, Ore.</p>
      </block>
